{"tid":793670,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加：我會坐北看台柴新領隊台！","createTime":"2018-08-25T15:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T15:08:38.000Z","uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e4dd3676242dc084a1ff799993f32d16de027a1f","tid":793670,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T15:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/1xopmJv5fWPtUSZ8Hh/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F1xopmJv5fWPtUSZ8Hh%2Fgiphy.gif&h=35d21f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=DdDrCGpX2awB3FpcnDWBngCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=d6ca03e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】阿仙奴領隊雲加於周日大勝般尼5:0後，除了發表告別感言外，還在記者會開玩笑說，「我會回來鬧新領隊。」<br />\n<br />\n帶領阿仙奴長達22年的雲加（Arsene Wenger）說到對未來的展望，「這對我來說是一個新的開始。我必須學會如何重新與自己聯繫，並組織我生活中的一切。 22年來，我不得不忘記自己的感受，去關心我需要解決的問題。」<br />\n<br />\n最後一次在酋長球場開賽後記者會的雲加，被問到日後會否回酋長球場觀看比賽時，他開玩笑說，「現在我有更多自己的時間了，我很樂意有一天去到北看台，然後我可以對下一任領隊大喊大叫！」<br />\n<br />\n「不過還要取決於我是否到其他地方工作，我的下一份工作是否會有時間讓我這樣做。」法國人續說。"},{"pid":"a97c7c9be6d3606a0970488285efddf1a354efd3","tid":793670,"uid":56649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T15:05:00.000Z","msg":"爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f72c6dc828c2a8977692c70dd59513582ed2fa","tid":793670,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T15:08:38.000Z","msg":"怨婦"}]}